This directory contains repository-local PDF support code for `markitdown-mb`.

Origin:
- Originally derived from the upstream MoonBit package `bobzhang/mbtpdf`
- Baseline vendoring source recorded by the repository as package version `0.1.2`

Current status:
- Maintained locally under `doc_parse/pdf/vendor/mbtpdf`
- Trimmed and adapted for this repository's PDF parsing/runtime needs
- Not maintained as a full upstream package mirror

Repository boundary:
- `doc_parse/pdf/raw` may import packages in this subtree directly
- Higher `doc_parse/pdf` and `convert/pdf` layers should depend on repository
  abstractions instead of exposing vendored package paths

Attribution and licensing:
- Upstream copyright and license terms remain governed by the preserved
  `LICENSE` file in this directory
- Local modifications in this repository are layered on top of that upstream
  codebase

Maintenance note:
- When pruning unused files from this subtree, keep the required provenance and
  license information intact even if package-local docs, scripts, or examples
  are removed
